OL,3,CPoliticians vote to allow assisted
OL,4,Cdying in Jersey
OL,6,FPoliticians also voted to ensure that
OL,7,Fmedical professionals have the right
OL,8,Fto refuse involvement in cases.
OL,10,FAn assisted dying law will now be
OL,11,Fdrafted by officials before it comes
OL,12,Fback to the States Assembly for final
OL,13,Fapproval, which is expected to happen
OL,14,Fin around 18 months.
OL,16,FThe earliest date an Assisted Dying
OL,17,FService could be up and running is
OL,18,Fbelieved to be 2027.
