OL,3,CPoliticians vote to allow assisted
OL,4,Cdying in Jersey
OL,6,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,7,FFarnham, told ITV News that robust
OL,8,Fsafeguards will be put in place to
OL,9,Fprotect islanders.
OL,11,FHe explained: "The safeguards we're
OL,12,Fgoing to have around this legislation
OL,13,Fare going to be at its very
OL,14,Ffoundation. We have good processes
OL,15,Flined up, supported by medical
OL,16,Fprofessionals and that is going to be
OL,17,Fkey.
OL,19,F"Members of the public can be
OL,20,Fconfident that we've given it full and
OL,21,Fdue consideration."
